The full AGPL-3.0 license text is available at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

Why AGPL-3.0-or-later: LibraForge imports audible (AGPL-3.0-only) and mutagen
(GPL-2.0-or-later) directly. Under copyleft, the combined work must carry the
strongest license. AGPL-3.0-or-later satisfies this. Because LibraForge is
already fully open-source, the AGPL network-service provision (source must be
available to users of the service) is automatically met.
